Package controller

Class ContactRecords

java.lang.Object
controller.ContactRecords
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ContactRecords extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
ContactRecords is the controller class for the Contact Records Screen. This screen allows for viewing of appointments separated by each of the three contacts. It contains FXML object fields and event handler methods to facilitate user interaction with the GUI.
